      "posted_at": 1784505669.413637,
      "text": "\ud83d\udea8 JUST IN: Zcash developed a new node designed to achieve privacy capabilities while processing transactions at speeds comparable to Visa's 50,000 per second capacity.\n(via CoinDesk)",
