    {
      "posted_at": 1784520058.947512,
      "text": "\ud83d\udea8 JUST IN: Citadel Securities just put $400M into Crypto.com -- and in the same news cycle, Base (Coinbase's blockchain network) handed its app over to Cobie, a well-known crypto podcaster and trader. \ud83d\udd04\ud83e\udd1d",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784530857.651972,
      "text": "\ud83d\udcb0 CRYPTO: Citadel Securities' $400M bet on Crypto.com wasn't a one-off -- Stripe is reportedly making a $53 billion move that could crown a stablecoin king.\n\nHere's the mechanism behind why Wall Street and payment giants keep circling stablecoins:",
