    {
      "posted_at": 1784535719.188184,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: US carries out ninth straight night of strikes on Iran, hitting the city of Bushehr. Iran fired back at bases in Syria, Kuwait and Jordan, and says it hit two tankers in the Strait of Hormuz.\n\nOil jumped over $91/barrel on the news.",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784535719.188184,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: Iran says not a single drop of oil or gas will pass through the Strait of Hormuz, as the US-Iran standoff enters its ninth night. Brent crude briefly topped $91 a barrel, its highest since June. \ud83d\udee2\ufe0f\u26a0\ufe0f",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784541664.713932,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: US strikes on Iran expand into a new phase -- a third US soldier has now died (in Iraq), and American forces hit Bushehr, home to Iran's only working nuclear power plant. \ud83d\udca5\u2622\ufe0f\n\nWhy it matters below:",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784541664.713932,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: Ukraine fired roughly 400 drones at Moscow overnight, after a weekend where Russia hit Kyiv with ballistic missiles and Ukraine struck warehouses outside Moscow. \ud83d\ude80\ud83d\udd25\n\nWhat this signals:",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784541664.713932,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: The UK gets its 7th PM in 10 years today -- Keir Starmer resigns, and Andy Burnham, fresh off winning the Labour leadership, is set to be invited by King Charles to form a government. \ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7\ud83d\udc51\n\nWhy this matters:",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784574060.887273,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: Andy Burnham has officially become the UK's new prime minister today, taking over from Keir Starmer as Labour hands the leadership baton to a new face. \ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7\ud83d\udd11\n\nWhy it matters below:",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784574060.887273,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: Russia's strikes on merchant ships in the Black Sea are intensifying -- 10 killed in the latest attacks, part of 28 deaths near Odesa this month alone. \ud83d\udea2\ud83d\udd25\n\nThe context:",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784574060.887273,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: Yemen's Houthi rebels just announced a 'maritime embargo' on Saudi Arabia, effective immediately, in response to a Saudi blockade of Yemeni ports and airports. \u2693\ud83d\udeab\n\nWhy it matters below:",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784585174.429159,
      "text": "Just saw this: Trump is slapping a 50% tariff on most Canadian goods -- autos, alcohol, dairy all hit. White House says Canada was \"discriminating\" against US products. Takes effect in 30 days. \ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8\ud83c\udde8\ud83c\udde6\ud83d\udcc9\n\nHoot hoot \ud83e\udd89",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784585174.429159,
      "text": "Okay, this one's heavy: the US just carried out its 10th straight night of strikes on Iran, and Trump is vowing revenge after American soldiers were killed. Both sides are still fighting over control of the Strait of Hormuz. \ud83d\udca5\ud83c\udf0a\n\nHoot hoot \ud83e\udd89",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784585613.628727,
      "text": "\ud83e\udd89 Well that was fast -- Andy Burnham's already picking his cabinet as UK PM: Rachel Reeves is out, Healey becomes chancellor, Miliband is foreign secretary, Yvette Cooper takes health, Rayner returns as housing secretary. \ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7\ud83d\udd01",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784592066.581041,
      "text": "\ud83d\udea8 JUST IN: Brazil's financial regulator established a task force with two months to develop a cryptocurrency tokenization framework.\n(via CoinDesk)",
      "url": "https://www.coindesk.com/policy/2026/07/20/brazil-s-securities-regulator-sets-up-task-force-with-60-day-deadline-for-tokenization-proposal"
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784592066.581041,
      "text": "\ud83d\udea8 JUST IN: Allbridge, a cross-chain protocol, suspended operations following a $1.65 million exploit using a flash loan attack.\n(via CoinDesk)",
      "url": "https://www.coindesk.com/business/2026/07/20/cross-chain-protocol-allbridge-halts-after-usd1-65-million-flash-loan-exploit"
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784606465.522188,
      "text": "\ud83e\udd89 Whoa, at least 27 people are dead and 83 still missing after a passenger ferry capsized off Guyana. An investigation just launched. \ud83d\udea2\ud83d\ude14",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784606465.522188,
      "text": "\ud83e\udd89 Trump just hit Canada with a 50% tariff on most goods -- wine, hockey sticks, cement, even stuff previously protected under the USMCA trade deal. Carney says Canada will 'intensify' talks. \ud83c\udde8\ud83c\udde6\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784628068.432297,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: Genuinely striking image out of Afghanistan -- flash floods just tore through Nuristan province, killing around 20 people and injuring more than 80. The city of Parun got hit hardest. \ud83c\udf27\ufe0f\ud83d\ude1f",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784628068.432297,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: Rough day for South China Sea tensions -- China and the Philippines just traded accusations after navy personnel clashed there, right before a big ASEAN (Southeast Asian nations) summit in Manila. \ud83d\udea2\u26a0\ufe0f",
      "url": null
    },
    {
      "posted_at": 1784628068.432297,
      "text": "\ud83c\udf0d WORLD: Didn't expect this one -- Australia's alpine resorts just smashed July heat records, up to 12C above average, right in the middle of ski season. Hotham, Falls Creek and Thredbo all set new highs. \ud83c\udfd4\ufe0f\ud83c\udf21\ufe0f",
      "url": null
    }
